title: NFL ATL: Week 7 recap
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Week 7 recap
description:
A room full of heroes, Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus and Chris Wesseling recap all of the Week 7 action and bring you the key takeaways and analysis from each game. Don’t miss another installment of “Win Wess’ Toaster” next episode.  Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.
